title: Scorpions - Unbreakable (2004)
description:
Unbreakable is the 15th studio album by the German rock/metal band Scorpions, released in 2004. In this album, Scorpions return to their original, more raw style of music after many concept albums and experimenting with different styles.
[Source: Wikipedia]

Released: June 22, 2004
Genre: Hard Rock/Heavy Metal
